{"TopicId":194297,"ForumId":38,"TopicTitle":"You get a million dollars but...","CreatedByName":"HCB-11","CreatedById":204956,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-30T06:24:48Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"HCB-11","CreatedById":204956,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-30T06:24:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou get a million dollars but for the rest of your life at random, you are suddenly teleported to a random time period.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor example, you are ordering a coffee at a Starbucks and suddenly *POOF* you get teleported to Berlin in 1945 just before the Soviets capture it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlthough after a certain amount of time you do get teleported back to where you came and you don\u0027t affect history.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould you take it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-05-30T07:01:36Z\u0022 title=\u002205/30/2020 07:01  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EMay 30, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by MarsBy2024OrBust\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EI forgot the \u0026quot;Would you take it\u0026quot; part. Oops.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fraston","CreatedById":188565,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-30T08:15:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223793625\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221590819888\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204956\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MarsBy2024OrBust\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, MarsBy2024OrBust said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou get a million dollars but for the rest of your life at random, you are suddenly teleported to a random time period.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor example, you are ordering a coffee at a Starbucks and suddenly *POOF* you get teleported to Berlin in 1945 just before the Soviets capture it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlthough after a certain amount of time you do get teleported back to where you came and you don\u0027t affect history.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould you take it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeems like a perfect example of what TVTropes.com calls \u201Cblessed with suck\u201D I\u2019d take the offer just because I could get so much more money\u00A0from predicting random events in the future, should I have access to a calendar in the pocket time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA powerful ability with the correct precautions, not even counting the million-dollar test reward.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-05-30T08:16:32Z\u0022 title=\u002205/30/2020 08:16  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EMay 30, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Fraston\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HCB-11","CreatedById":204956,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-30T10:05:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223793647\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221590826551\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188565\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fraston\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Fraston said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI could get so much more money\u00A0from predicting random events in the future, should I have access to a calendar in the pocket time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Screen_Shot_2019-06-05_at_1.26.32_PM.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.31\u0022 height=\u0022446\u0022 width=\u0022792\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.kym-cdn.com/entries/icons/original/000/029/959/Screen_Shot_2019-06-05_at_1.26.32_PM.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HansonKerman","CreatedById":185809,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-02T17:15:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003Eno that\u2019s annoying\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-03T05:52:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223793625\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221590819888\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204956\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MarsBy2024OrBust\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/30/2020 at 9:24 AM, MarsBy2024OrBust said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*POOF* you get teleported to Berlin in 1945 just before the Soviets capture it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike if Berlin \u0026lt;1945 a million of American dolars would cause fewer questions...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-03T19:37:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow far does this time travel go? Are we talking the latest century? Or am I going to find myself wading through a Permian swamp with Dimetrodons?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-03T20:20:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou get a million dollars (USD),\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTyxwc1NE-c7BtKqXWGE1t\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002286.72\u0022 height=\u0022209\u0022 width=\u0022241\u0022 src=\u0022https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTyxwc1NE-c7BtKqXWGE1tY_yM2E3YfJcwdMrqeu72L0nn7CwnS\u0026amp;usqp=CAU\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nbuy a pack of Georgian tea (not from Georgia, but from Georgia)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022QPwaEsmoZNdssk_avPsxbIh-8yMbAWZILd0b2jY2\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.41\u0022 height=\u0022340\u0022 width=\u0022512\u0022 src=\u0022https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/QPwaEsmoZNdssk_avPsxbIh-8yMbAWZILd0b2jY2qxF5wenUXkWM7ndoWgm1_SpNoyoVtdTF6iw7aXCj85X-QGU4kNgrplT0eUWKNzH93w\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nand appear in the George III palace where he is giving an audience to the East India Company managers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey wonder, what is this tea, who are these strangely familiar people on the banknotes, and who has printed them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HCB-11","CreatedById":204956,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-04T01:03:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223796425\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591213070\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150330\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cubinator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, cubinator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow far does this time travel go? Are we talking the latest century? Or am I going to find myself wading through a Permian swamp with Dimetrodons?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically any point in time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-04T01:03:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223796614\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591232592\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204956\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MarsBy2024OrBust\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, MarsBy2024OrBust said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically any point in time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGreat, so I need to wear a spacesuit. No thanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fraston","CreatedById":188565,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-09T07:21:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223796616\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591232636\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150330\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cubinator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 6/3/2020 at 8:03 PM, cubinator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGreat, so I need to wear a spacesuit. No thanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*calling NASA*\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u201CSooo, I need to rent a space suit\u201D\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u201CWe don\u2019t do that, you crazy person.\u201D\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u201CNo, you don\u2019t see-I have a funky ability that warps me into a different time and after a while warps me back.\u201D\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u201DI\u2019m calling shenanigans here\u201D\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u201CNo, just this morning I saw \u0026lt;very specific thing not known yet about an important historical event:\u0026gt;\u201D\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u201CWh-\u201C\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HansonKerman","CreatedById":185809,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-09T19:02:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EIs it proportional to the movement of the earth or do you just usually end up in space where the Earth was. Also, what if you\u2019re teleported to the death of the universe and die from not existing\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223796614\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591232592\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204956\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MarsBy2024OrBust\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 6/3/2020 at 9:03 PM, MarsBy2024OrBust said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically any point in time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003Eas in being in the future\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-06-09T19:03:02Z\u0022 title=\u002206/09/2020 07:03  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EJune 9, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by HansonKerman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}